---
title: Rockfish Piccata with Capers, Israeli Couscous Pilaf and Sauteed Spinach
description: Typically made with chicken, we’re giving rockfishi a “piccata” twist. A savoury butter sauce of briny capers, thyme, and lemon lends the dish its characteristic flavour.
